github.setup        HeddleCo heddle 0.6.0 v
github.tarball_from archive
revision            0

homepage            https://heddle.sh

description         AI-native version control CLI with Git interoperability

long_description    Heddle is an AI-native version control system that \
                    maintains its own state model while providing Git \
                    interoperability. It features thread-first agent \
                    workflows, content-addressed immutable history, \
                    provenance-aware inspection, and semantic diff and \
                    merge at the AST-item level for Rust, Python, \
                    JavaScript, and TypeScript.

